<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v15" title="Q28_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una planta embotelladora se utiliza una máquina llenadora para llenar botellas de jugo a una rapidez constante.</p>
    <p>Esta rapidez <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, medida en botellas por hora (botellas/h), se modela con la expresión
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>r</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mi>N</m:mi>
          <m:mi>t</m:mi>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>,
      donde <m:math><m:mi>N</m:mi></m:math> es el número total de botellas llenadas y <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el tiempo, en horas, durante el cual la máquina funciona para llenar esas botellas.</p>
    <p>En un ciclo de prueba, la máquina llenó completamente <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> botellas en <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> minutos, manteniendo rapidez constante. Según el modelo anterior, ¿cuál es la rapidez <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math> de la máquina, en botellas por hora (botellas/h)?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">300 botellas/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En 30 minutos la máquina llena 600 botellas, y 30 minutos equivalen a 0,5 horas. Entonces, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> botellas/h. Por lo tanto, 300 botellas/h no coincide con el modelo dado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1200 botellas/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como 30 minutos equivalen a 0,5 horas, se aplica <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso la rapidez de la máquina es 1200 botellas/h.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">600 botellas/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El tiempo debe expresarse en horas. Como 30 minutos = 0,5 horas, la rapidez es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> botellas/h. Por lo tanto, 600 botellas/h no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">20 botellas/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con el modelo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> y usando <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> en horas, 30 minutos = 0,5 horas. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> botellas/h. Por lo tanto, 20 botellas/h no corresponde a la rapidez de la máquina.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los datos del problema</strong></p>
            <p>El número total de botellas llenadas es <m:math><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>El tiempo de funcionamiento es <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> minutos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir el tiempo a horas</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula usa el tiempo en horas, por lo que se debe convertir <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> minutos a horas.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>÷</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,5</m:mn></m:math> horas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Aplicar la fórmula de rapidez</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>r</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mi>N</m:mi>
                    <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>600</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0,5</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>600</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>÷</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1200</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La rapidez de la máquina es <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math> botellas por hora.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>1200 botellas/h</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>